OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Florida has approved controversial new 
OL,6, standards for teaching African American
OL,7, history at the state's public schools. 
OL,9,FThe updated guidelines include a       
OL,10,Frequirement that students learn "how   
OL,11,Fslaves developed skills which, in some 
OL,12,Finstances, could be applied for their  
OL,13,Fpersonal benefit".                     
OL,15,FCritics called the new guidelines      
OL,16,F"sanitized" and "a big step backward". 
OL,18,FFlorida's education commissioner has   
OL,19,Fdenied the lessons will shy away from  
OL,20,F"the tougher subjects".                
